										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Sometimes, when you want to change the color of an image, you will confuse how to adjust it(especially who have problem with reading the display of colors). There is a feature in Samsung Galaxy S5 named <strong>Color adjustment</strong> that provides this functions. When enable this feature, you can adjust easily by drag/move the bar. Now we will study how to use it.</p>
<p><a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20-e1419655689358.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-138" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-28-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-28" width="168" height="300" />      <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-139" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2014-12-27-03-48-20" width="168" height="300" /></a>  <a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-213" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-168x300.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46" width="168" height="300" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-168x300.png 168w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46-576x1024.png 576w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-03-04-03-46.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-235" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27-300x168.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27" width="300" height="168" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27-300x169.png 300w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-27.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />   <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-231" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-41-300x168.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-41" width="300" height="168" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-41-300x169.png 300w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-41-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-13-41.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-233" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26-300x168.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26" width="300" height="168" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26-300x169.png 300w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-26.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>    <a href="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-232" src="http://sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22-300x168.png" alt="Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22" width="300" height="168" srcset="https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22-300x169.png 300w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.sprogroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Screenshot_2015-01-06-14-14-22.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<p>How to use:</p>
<ol>
<li>Swipe down the top of screen to open the <strong>notification panel</strong> and then tap to <strong>setting</strong> icon</li>
<li>From the setting function, select <strong>Device</strong> Tag and scroll down to <strong>Personalization</strong> section and then tap to <strong>Accessibility</strong>.</li>
<li>Select <strong>Vision</strong></li>
<li>Select <strong>Color adjustment</strong> and enable this feature.</li>
<li>Tap to <strong>Start</strong> button</li>
<li>Arrange the provided color tiles in order of similarity, starting from the fixed color on the bottom panel. Tap the color that is most similar with the previous one.</li>
<li>Select <strong>Done</strong> button</li>
<li>If you can&#8217;t distinguish the colours, tap <strong>Camera</strong>or <strong>Image</strong>.</li>
<li>Slide the <strong>color adjustment</strong> bar to the left or to the right to fine-tune the color.</li>
<li>Tap to <strong>Done</strong> button</li>
<li>The colours have been adjusted and changed into more recognizable colours.</li>
</ol>
<p>Above steps are used to enable enable/configure <strong>Color Adjustment</strong> in Samsung Galaxy S5. Hope it is helpful for you.</p>
